org.dellroad.stuff.vaadin8

Annotation Type FieldBuilder.DateTimeField


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Documented
public static @interface FieldBuilder.DateTimeField
    Specifies how a Java property should be edited using an DateTimeField.
    See Also:
    FieldBuilder.AbstractDateField, FieldBuilder
